comments: Bridges (PHX) makes marginal contact with Leonard (LAC) after his release on his driving shot attempt.
George (LAC) briefly slides his arm across Ayton's (PHX) upper body during the screen.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal picking position in George's (LAC) path.
Zubac (LAC) makes contact with Ayton's (PHX) arm during his play at the basket.
Jackson (LAC) makes marginal contact with Bridges (PHX) during the pick and does not affect Bridges' ability to defend.
Rubio (PHX) makes contact with Leonard's (LAC) arm and affects his SQBR on the perimeter.
Jackson (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Bridges (PHX) path.
Leonard (LAC) keeps a collapsed forearm and does not extend it to Bridges (PHX) during his step-back on the perimeter.
Booker (PHX) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Zubac's (LAC) path.
George (LAC) makes marginal contact with Rubio's (PHX) arm and doesn't affect his ability to pass.
Ayton (PHX) and Zubac (LAC) engage and disengage during the rebound.
George (LAC) makes marginal contact with Rubio (PHX) in the post and doesn't affect his ability to defend.
Ayton (PHX) is drawn into the air, but remains vertical. George (LAC) then initiates the contact by leaning into Ayton during his driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) makes marginal contact with Zubac (LAC) as both players engage and separate during the rebound.
Booker (PHX) makes marginal contact with Zubac (LAC) during his put-back shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Jackson's (LAC) path.
Jackson (LAC) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) makes marginal contact and goes to, but not through, Bridges (PHX) during the drive.
Ayton (PHX) jumps A to B and delivers contact to Leonard's (LAC) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) hooks George's (LAC) arm and affects his ability to defend.
Jackson (LAC) momentarily places a hand to Rubio's (PHX) front and immediately removes it. The reaction is not commensurate with the level of contact.
Leonard (LAC) legally contest Rubio's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
George (LAC) does not make contact with Booker's (PHX) arm during his swipe.
George (LAC) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt and makes incidental contact during his follow-through.
